    surveydata.Rd

    Various processed survey datasets.

    Format

    biomass: Design-based biomass estimates. A data frame.

    science_center

    Name of the U.S. Science Center.

    region

    U.S. region.

    area

    Survey name indicating the region of the data.

    common_name

    Species common name.

    scientific_name

    Species scientific name.

    year

    Year.

    est

    Mean biomass estimate.

    lwr

    Lower bound of the biomass estimated base on 95% confidence interval.

    uwr

    Upper bound of the biomass estimated base on 95% confidence interval.

    parameters: Estimated growth parameters. A list of two data frames.

    region

    U.S. region.

    common_name

    Species common name.

    sex

    Sex (Female, Male, Unsexed).

    k

    Estimated von Bertanlaffy growth rate.

    Linf

    Estimated maximimum size in cm.

    L0

    Estimated minimum size at in cm.

    CV1

    Estimated coefficient of variation around L0.

    CV2

    Estimated coefficient of variation around Linf.

    median_intercept

    Median values for the length-mass intercept parameter (A).

    SD

    Estimated standard deviation for length-mass relationship.

    A

    Length-mass intercept A (A * length_cm ^ B).

    B

    Length-mass exponential parameter B (A * length_cm ^ B).

    specimens: Biological data. A data frame.

    science_center

    Name of the U.S. Science Center.

    region

    U.S. region.

    survey_id

    Survey name indicating the region of the data.

    common_name

    Species common name.

    scientific_name

    Species scientific name.

    year

    Year.

    sex

    Sex (Female, Male, Unsexed).

    length_cm

    Length of fish in cm.

    age_years

    Age of fish in year.

    mass_kg

    Mass of fish in kg.

    length_comps: Expanded length comps. A data frame.

    science_center

    Name of the U.S. Science Center.

    region

    U.S. region.

    area

    Survey name indicating the region of the data.

    common_name

    Species common name.

    scientific_name

    Species scientific name.

    year

    Year.

    sex

    Sex (Female, Male, Unsexed).

    length_cm

    Length of fish in cm.

    population_count

    Expanded observations by length.

    total

    Sum of the expanded length observations by year across all sexes.

    propotion

    Proportion of observations by length and sex that sums to 100 for each year across all observed sexes.

    age_comps: Expanded age comps. A data frame.

    science_center

    Name of the U.S. Science Center.

    region

    U.S. region.

    area

    Survey name indicating the region of the data.

    common_name

    Species common name.

    scientific_name

    Species scientific name.

    year

    Year.

    sex

    Sex (Female, Male, Unsexed).

    age_years

    Age of the fish in years.

    population_count

    Expanded observations by age.

    total

    Sum of the expanded age observations by year across all sexes.

    propotion

    Proportion of observations by age and sex that sums to 100 for each year across all observed sexes.
